Batista Says Colombia Coal Unit Public Offering May Raise Up to $5 Billion

-- B y   C r i s t i a n e   L u c c h e s i   a n d   J o s u e   L e o n e l
-- 
2011-08-27T19:01:27Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-27/batista-says-colombia-coal-unit-public-offering-may-raise-up-to-5-billion.html
Brazilian billionaire  Eike Batista 
said an initial public offering of his Colombia coal unit may
raise $4 billion to $5 billion.  He spoke today at an event in Campos do Jordao, Brazil.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Cristiane Lucchesi in Sao Paulo at 
